{"translation-revision-date":"2026-03-27 09:00:36+0000","generator":"GlotPress\/4.0.3","domain":"messages","locale_data":{"messages":{"":{"domain":"messages","plural-forms":"nplurals=3; plural=(n % 10 == 1 && n % 100 != 11) ? 0 : ((n % 10 >= 2 && n % 10 <= 4 && (n % 100 < 12 || n % 100 > 14)) ? 1 : 2);","lang":"hr"},"Menu Switcher Layout":["Izgled izmjenjiva\u010da jezika"],"Additional Settings":["Dodatne postavke"],"Shortcode":["Kratki kod"],"Use shortcode on any page or widget. You can also add the Language Switcher Block in the WP Gutenberg Editor.":["Koristite kratki kod na bilo kojoj stranici ili widgetu. Tako\u0111er mo\u017eete dodati blok izmjenjiva\u010da jezika u WP Gutenberg editoru."],"Copy":["Kopiraj"],"Copied!":["Kopirano!"],"This option only works when exactly two languages are published.":["Ova opcija funkcionira samo kada su objavljena to\u010dno dva jezika."],"Transforms the language switcher into a button showing the other available language, not the current one. <br> Only works when there are exactly two languages, the default one and a translation one.":["Transformira jezi\u010dni izmjenjiva\u010d u gumb koji prikazuje drugi dostupni jezik, a ne trenutni. <br> Radi samo kad postoje to\u010dno dva jezika, zadani i jedan prevedeni."],"Go to <a href=\"\/wp-admin\/nav-menus.php\">Appearance \u2192 Menus<\/a> to add languages to the Language Switcher in any menu.<br> <a href=\"https:\/\/translatepress.com\/docs\/settings\/language-switcher\/?utm_source=tp-language-switcher&utm_medium=client-site&utm_campaign=ls-menu-item#menu-switcher\" target=\"_blank\">Learn more in our documentation.<\/a>":["Idite na <a href=\"\/wp-admin\/nav-menus.php\">Izgled \u2192 Izbornici<\/a> kako biste dodali jezike u izmjenjiva\u010d jezika u bilo kojem izborniku.<br><a href=\"https:\/\/translatepress.com\/docs\/settings\/language-switcher\/?utm_source=tp-language-switcher&utm_medium=client-site&utm_campaign=ls-menu-item#menu-switcher\" target=\"_blank\">Saznajte vi\u0161e u na\u0161oj dokumentaciji.<\/a>"],"Switcher animations":["Animacije izmjenjiva\u010da"],"You have unsaved changes. Leave anyway?":["Imate nespremljene promjene. Svejedno napusti?"],"Show the small Powered by TranslatePress label in the language switcher.":["Prika\u017ei malu oznaku Powered by TranslatePress u jezi\u010dnom izmjenjiva\u010du."],"Show opposite language":["Prika\u017ei suprotan jezik"],"Customize Layout":["Prilagodite izgled"],"Enable custom CSS":["Omogu\u0107i prilago\u0111eni CSS"],"Flag icons border radius":["Ikone zastava i radijus granica"],"Square (1:1)":["Kvadrat (1:1)"],"Rectangle (4:3)":["Pravokutnik (4:3)"],"Flag icons shape":["Oblik ikona zastave"],"Large":["Velika"],"Normal":["Normalna"],"Flag and text size":["Veli\u010dina zastave i teksta"],"Switcher border radius":["Radijus ruba izmjenjiva\u010da"],"Switcher border width":["\u0160irina ruba izmjenjiva\u010da"],"Switcher border color":["Boja ruba izmjenjiva\u010da"],"Text hover color":["Boja lebdenja teksta"],"Text color":["Boja teksta"],"Background hover color":["Pozadinska boja lebdenja"],"Background color":["Boja pozadine"],"Customize Design":["Prilagodite dizajn"],"Show languages side by side":["Prika\u017ei jezike jedan pored drugog"],"Show languages as dropdown":["Prika\u017ei jezike kao padaju\u0107i izbornik"],"Switcher Type":["Vrsta izmjenjiva\u010da"],"Switcher is disabled":["Izmjenjiva\u010d je onemogu\u0107en"],"Switcher is enabled":["Izmjenjiva\u010d je omogu\u0107en"],"Enable Floating Switcher":["Omogu\u0107ite plutaju\u0107i izmjenjiva\u010d"],"Switcher Preview":["Pregled izmjenjiva\u010da"],"Keep editing":["Nastavite s ure\u0111ivanjem"],"Restoring will revert to the last saved version and discard your current edits.":["Vra\u0107anje \u0107e se vratiti na zadnju spremljenu verziju i odbaciti va\u0161e trenutne izmjene."],"Revert changes":["Poni\u0161ti promjene"],"Revert to last saved values":["Povratak na posljednje spremljene vrijednosti"],"Save changes":["Spremi promjene"],"Saving...":["Spremam..."],"Hover over the language switcher to see it in action!":["Pre\u0111ite mi\u0161em preko jezi\u010dnog prekida\u010da da ga vidite u akciji!"],"Apply %s preset":["Primijenite %s unaprijed postavljeno"],"Apply preset":["Primjeni unaprijed postavljeno"],"It will override your current settings.":["To \u0107e nadja\u010dati tvoje trenutne postavke."],"Open the language switcher shortcode by clicking on it instead of hovering. <br> Close it by clicking on it, anywhere else on the screen or by pressing the escape key. <br> This will affect only the shortcode language switcher.":["Otvori kratki kod za promjenu jezika klikom na njega umjesto lebdenja. <br> Zatvorite ga klikom na njega, bilo gdje drugdje na ekranu ili pritiskom tipke izlaz. <br> To \u0107e utjecati samo na izmjenjiva\u010d jezika kratkog koda."],"Apply a preset":["Primijenite unaprijed postavljeno"],"Revert":["Vrati prethodno"],"Cancel":["Otka\u017ei"],"Are you sure you want to apply the <strong>%s<\/strong> preset?":["Jesi li siguran da \u017eeli\u0161 primijeniti unaprijed postavljeno<strong>%s<\/strong>?"],"Transparent":["Transparentno"],"Border":["Rub"],"Default":["Zadano"],"Open language switcher only on click":["Otvori prekida\u010d jezika samo na klik"],"Dark":["Tamno"],"Show \"Powered by TranslatePress\"":["Prika\u017ei \"Pokre\u0107e TranslatePress\""],"Saved!":["Spremljeno!"]}},"comment":{"reference":"assets\/js\/trp-lang-switcher-configurator.js"}}